title: Good for Cows
text:
Good For Cows is an experimental jazz band from Oakland, United States. Their line-up consists of Xiu Xiu's former drummer Ches Smith
 and former Xiu Xiu bassist Devin Hoff.


== Beginning ==
Band claims they formed in Oakland, CA in 1999 "when no one else would show up for band practice".
